First thing first i want to explain what is php ? what can you do with php ?

PHP is a server scripting language, and a powerful tool for making dynamic and interactive Web pages
PHP is a widely-used, free, and efficient alternative to competitors such as Microsoft's ASP
PHP 7 is the latest stable release

While useing php we should already know HTML CSS and javascript

What can Php do ?

encrypt data
collect form data
send and receive cookies
add, delete, modify data in your database
be used to control user-access
generate dynamic page content

Why PHP ?
PHP is compatible with almost all servers used today 
PHP runs on various platforms (Windows, Linux, Unix, Mac OS)
